author: David Furones
title: Calvary ousts U-School for first regional final berth - Sun Sentinel
text:
Calvary ousts U-School for first regional final berth Calvary reaction after regional semifinal win over U-School 
Calvary Christian coach Cilk McSweeney and guard Jerald Butler discuss the Eagles' 51-46 regional semifinal win over University School and center Victor Uyaelunmo reacts to upcoming matchup against former team Gulliver.
